Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.80,0:00:08.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作為懲罰 命令他們兩個去買零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.17,0:00:13.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說他們在這麼冷的天裡出去買東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.85,0:00:17.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 今天可是很冷的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.02,0:00:20.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說你看起來穿得很冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉 好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.90,0:00:26.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛就不用關心啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.61,0:00:31.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來打擾啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.24,0:00:35.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.00,0:00:38.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要調戲我家實玖瑠的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.54,0:00:45.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先來把我放倒了再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要跟我決鬥的意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.72,0:00:58.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在活動室裡禁止戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧 社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.08,0:01:02.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 實玖瑠太可愛了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.90,0:01:09.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那心情 我能理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.44,0:01:10.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能理解啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.65,0:01:13.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在自動販賣機旁掉有實瑠的話 會撿起來對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是貓咪比喻還是零錢比喻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.16,0:01:18.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.99,0:01:22.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然無視我家長門就討論可愛東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.21,0:01:23.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要跟他們較勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 我接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 接受你的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.01,0:01:34.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門睡覺的時候要是對她說話的話會叫我「媽媽」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會感冒的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,媽媽 再讓我睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？這不是比喻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.14,0:01:41.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說那是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.73,0:01:45.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠追貓咪的話會撞到電線桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仰望天空的話掉水溝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且百發百中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說得好像我每天都會那樣似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.65,0:01:54.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖說偶爾會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.20,0:01:58.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼 長門每天在浴室的鏡子前確認肚子的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.83,0:01:59.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是什麼害羞的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.87,0:02:03.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然你都說的這麼徹底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我要丟大招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠的胸前有個星形的黑痣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出來了 我不知道的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.51,0:02:12.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真有你的 鶴屋學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然拿出連本人都不知道的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.18,0:02:22.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦？這樣下去的話要輸了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不要煽動她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.94,0:02:29.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉 算了吧 你不會有奇怪的情報對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.82,0:02:30.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.82,0:02:34.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.95,0:02:39.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了即將來臨的情人節偷偷的買了材料 藏起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.67,0:02:48.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,享受節日是好事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:54.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是喔 完全不是害羞的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有偷偷做的必要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.92,Title - blur,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(897,880)\bord0\blur10\fad(695,695)}成為我的戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.92,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(695,695)\pos(897,880)}成為我的戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}平安時代的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.07,0:04:42.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}雖說門第跟財富都很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}但不管怎麼說不會和歌就不受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.03,0:04:50.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}因為那時是用和歌互通書信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很痛啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.50,0:05:08.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}聽好囉 求出拋物線與直線的交點坐標要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.95,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\org(1361.6,301.6)\frx4\fry2\pos(1368,316)\frz336.4}情人節手工甜點特輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.19,0:05:22.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特地出來門口來等我 真是相當用心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,委員會那有正作 好像來不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊 那正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門跟朝倉也好像有事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就我一個在活動室裡也沒事做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以今天休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.08,0:05:44.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣 為了不讓你非法入侵學校而在這等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:51.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真·社長的我都沒問過就擅自休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非法社員的你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是13號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才休息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 那邊的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.82,0:06:08.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 女學生 我可是很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別磨磨蹭蹭的了 跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.78,0:06:13.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.83,0:06:14.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:16.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到哪去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 雖然我想開始做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這材料可真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都說機會是自己過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那都已經過時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是過不過時的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.94,0:06:44.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被稱為不可思議的物品跟現象是不會那麼容易出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.94,0:06:48.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而把他們找出來才有意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:48.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.36,0:06:55.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以啊 我們必須主動的去找 不斷的發現它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.29,0:07:01.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它們也肯定想著被發現 一直在等著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.54,0:07:06.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如說它們想著永遠的安眠不想被打擾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去把這世界的不可思議找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.09,0:07:10.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在哪找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.84,0:07:12.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.64,0:07:19.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道也會用不知道的方法把它找出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.93,0:07:20.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,懂了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之先是腳踏實地的做市內搜尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你將能成為新歷史的開拓者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 你想怎樣就怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的 準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 我還沒問呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是想做怎樣的巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.67,0:07:54.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以這些材料來看 應該是挺簡單的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:08:08.13,S2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1056,124)}長門有希的料理教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,融化 倒入 撒入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後就讓它成型後的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明是很簡單的步驟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但讓這孩子一人來做的話 感覺會失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.28,0:08:14.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,簡單是不錯啦 要不要來點複雜的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,例如♥形的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊不 不用到那地步也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.87,0:08:26.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太簡單的話也沒有我幫忙的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.38,0:08:32.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 那麼先把巧克力融了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.36,0:08:55.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.32,0:08:58.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.02,0:09:18.03,S2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1067.2,124)}真正的\N朝倉涼子的料理教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上就錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡我們要隔水加熱來融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.51,0:09:14.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隔水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不這麼做的話巧克力不好融化的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厲害 真的能融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.85,0:09:26.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來需要幫忙的地方很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 這可是2月的河流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 會感冒的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,該上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再找找 要找到河童為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.26,0:09:55.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別走太遠了啊 摔跤了就會死的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題 沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.82,0:10:20.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是有心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.91,0:10:27.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.08,0:10:31.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,腳 很冷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.02,0:10:54.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也知道冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你給我記住喔 你這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恨死你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣子對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 棒極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.17,0:11:20.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你覺得真的有河童嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰知道 可能真的有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春日？春日！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夠了吧 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.92,0:11:55.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 區區阿虛 竟然敢先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛！什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天要去哪裡尋找呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:00.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是服了你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於做好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼就放進冰箱讓它們成型吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.85,0:12:10.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行不行 絕對不能熬夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.67,0:12:44.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 就和平常一樣晚上睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回過神來已經早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:52.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈哈哈哈 這孩子真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趕緊去給我洗臉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 快點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說 你打算什麼時候把巧克力送出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然還是社團活動的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.01,0:13:31.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必須讓你們2個獨處啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,獨處？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對對 去把阿虛叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 困難很大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打起精神來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論怎樣都是要跨過送巧克力這個障礙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無非是稍微變難了些 別在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為 無論變得有多困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都會送出去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我會送出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,期待已久的情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.35,0:14:13.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不覺得有什麼不對嗎 阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谷口 過甚的期待只會加深你的絕望哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,♬今天的午飯是巧克力♬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不覺得有什麼不對嗎 阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.57,0:14:35.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谷口 放棄可以防止自己白白受傷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.91,0:14:38.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早啊 要去吃飯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝喵沒和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.13,0:14:50.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋 不要突然跑起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和朝倉約在社團活動室會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那今天就在文藝社吃午餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠 可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我倒是沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們去真的可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天我們教室裡面的氣氛很緊張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不太方便吃飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.87,0:15:19.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,氣氛緊張？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天可是情人節啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人們的眼神都變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋 你太大驚小怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.97,0:15:35.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不 這樣的話如果連一點巧克力都不送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就沒辦法收場囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是實玖瑠粉絲俱樂部就有三位數了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還真是具體…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道…應該沒準備巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼不否定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.36,0:15:53.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個雖然是必然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收巧克力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.54,0:16:02.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是在期待收到自己喜歡的人的巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是肯定的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,假裝並不期待這個露骨的節日然後突然襲擊什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不就是最好的證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.76,0:16:11.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 除此以外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都只能算成麻煩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊不 並不是那樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我們是人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:27.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然有喜歡 一般 討厭 這些想法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 那種事無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.45,0:16:37.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為那不過是送出巧克力的人的自我滿足嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.57,0:16:39.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了自己而送出去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要介意對方的想法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝著他的胸口 用力扔過去就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可不能亂扔東西哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊真是的 忘記買飲料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.13,0:16:59.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去買一下 你們先吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該很快就會回來 我們就先吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的 我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.80,S3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算不對話也能吃飯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.68,S4,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很焦慮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:23.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才鶴屋說的那些是在鼓勵你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對不是什麼欺負人哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過說的稍微極端了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 要是換做是我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.39,0:17:47.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我要是男生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收到了長門的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的會非常開心的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼好像我在表白一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法好好表達 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 我聽到了哦 夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也真真切切地聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把那個當成是表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也沒什麼問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠 我有些不太說得出口的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門的內心已經完全被阿虛佔領了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡好像有個很大的誤會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要偷聽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來的路上遇到鶴屋學姐 一起走到門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發現你們就像少女漫畫那樣互相對視著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍不住就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.53,0:18:46.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後就靠眼神的交流來守護著你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這兩個人 思考回路是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像寶冢劇團一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.22,0:18:59.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.38,0:19:03.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被學姐們鼓勵之後 鼓起勇氣了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,決戰就在放學後囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 我們就先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.98,0:19:16.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:29.60,S5,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(356.8,156)\frz24.5}情人節大作戰！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 我來講解一下今天的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要好好聽清楚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.12,0:19:30.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把社團活動室的鑰匙交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放學之後 我把這個鑰匙給阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並拜託他來開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在阿虛打開門的這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門過去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 多麼不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.89,0:19:53.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,社團活動室裡面就是長門和阿虛兩人的空間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這之後 我會慢一點到活動室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.15,0:20:05.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 現在就這樣要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題嗎 能做到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.37,0:20:15.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 就算不用這麼故意地設計成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.58,0:20:19.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我盡快到活動室等他不是也可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 你稍微自己思考一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓阿虛在活動室裡等自己過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和自己忐忑不安的等阿虛的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底哪個比較容易做好心理準備呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.49,0:20:45.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 還是我過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣 就算多費一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也要做好心理準備 把巧克力送出去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.41,0:20:53.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.13,0:21:02.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟是那麼努力做出來的巧克力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.56,0:21:13.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊哈 結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.68,0:21:17.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被打落了失意的深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.35,0:21:18.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.65,0:21:19.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,國木田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.81,0:21:22.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也只是收到了明顯是義理的巧克力而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用力扔過去就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的會非常開心的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.71,0:21:43.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟是那麼努力做出來的巧克力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來晚了真是抱歉
